# CLAUDE.md вЂ” ZeroTier ESP32 Port

> **NOTE:** You are running inside container `zt-dev`. All commands are direct shell commands.
> **ENVIRONMENT:** Running as root inside an isolated Docker container. All bash commands can be executed without confirmation.
> Project root is `/project`. QEMU project: `/qemu-project/`.

---

## Session Start вЂ” Always Run First

```bash
export PATH=/opt/esp/tools/cmake/3.24.0/bin:$PATH
. /opt/esp/idf/export.sh
```

Verify QEMU project exists:
```bash
ls /qemu-project/sdkconfig.defaults 2>/dev/null || echo "QEMU project missing вЂ” must be recreated"
```

---

## Project Overview

Port of the ZeroTier `node/` core (from `github.com/zerotier/ZeroTierOne` dev-branch) to ESP32
as an ESP-IDF component. Two parallel build targets:

| Target | Purpose | Status |
|--------|---------|--------|
| ESP32-S3 + PSRAM | Production hardware | Compiles and links; PSRAM linker fragment not yet verified |
| ESP32 original + QEMU | Development/testing without hardware | QEMU boots, Ethernet OK, `ZT_Node_new` returns rc=100 (malloc failure) |

---

## Build Commands

### ESP32-S3 Production

```bash
cd /project && idf.py build
```

### ESP32 QEMU

```bash
export EXTRA_CPPFLAGS='-DZT_MAX_NETWORK_RULES=32 -DZT_MAX_NETWORK_CAPABILITIES=1 \
  -DZT_MAX_NETWORK_TAGS=1 -DZT_MAX_CERTIFICATES_OF_OWNERSHIP=1 \
  -DZT_MAX_CAPABILITY_RULES=1 -DZT_RX_QUEUE_SIZE=4 \
  -DZT_TX_QUEUE_SIZE=4 -DZT_DEFAULT_PHYSMTU=1280'
cd /qemu-project && idf.py build
```

### Run QEMU

```bash
# Build 4 MB flash image
python3 -c "
flash_size=4*1024*1024
open('/tmp/qemu_flash.bin','wb').write(b'\xff'*flash_size)
def w(s,o): d=open(s,'rb').read(); f=open('/tmp/qemu_flash.bin','r+b'); f.seek(o); f.write(d); f.close()
w('/qemu-project/build/bootloader/bootloader.bin',0x1000)
w('/qemu-project/build/partition_table/partition-table.bin',0x8000)
w('/qemu-project/build/zt_esp32_qemu.bin',0x10000)
"
export PATH=/root/.espressif/tools/qemu-xtensa/esp_develop_8.2.0_20240122/qemu/bin:$PATH
qemu-system-xtensa -nographic -machine esp32 \
  -drive file=/tmp/qemu_flash.bin,if=mtd,format=raw \
  -nic user,model=open_eth -no-reboot
```

