## Patches Applied to ZeroTierOne Source

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| `node/Mutex.hpp` | `#if defined(ESP_PLATFORM)` block вЂ” FreeRTOS `SemaphoreHandle_t` replaces pthreads |
| `node/NetworkConfig.hpp` | `#ifdef ZT_NETWORKCONFIG_DICT_CAPACITY_OVERRIDE` вЂ” allows reduced Dictionary capacity |
| `node/Utils.cpp` | `randomBuf[65536]` в†’ `randomBuf[256]` вЂ” reduces BSS by 64 KB |
| `include/ZeroTierOne.h` | `#ifndef` guards on `ZT_MAX_NETWORK_RULES`, `ZT_MAX_NETWORK_CAPABILITIES`, `ZT_MAX_NETWORK_TAGS`, `ZT_MAX_CERTIFICATES_OF_OWNERSHIP`, `ZT_MAX_CAPABILITY_RULES` |
| `node/Constants.hpp` | `ZT_RX_QUEUE_SIZE`, `ZT_TX_QUEUE_SIZE`, `ZT_MAX_PACKET_FRAGMENTS` already had `#ifndef` guards |

**Pending patch (next step):**
```c
// Constants.hpp ~line 290 вЂ” add before existing ZT_DEFAULT_PHYSMTU definition
#ifndef ZT_DEFAULT_PHYSMTU
#define ZT_DEFAULT_PHYSMTU 1500
#endif
```

