## Stub Files

All stubs reside under `/project/components/zerotier_node/port/stubs/`:

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `prometheus/simpleapi.h` | Full prometheus-cpp stub: `Counter`, `Gauge`, `Histogram<T>`, `BuilderT<T>`, `CustomFamily<T>`, all operators, `Add(map)`, `Add(map, vector)`, `SaveToFile`, `registry` |
| `prometheus/histogram.h`, `registry.h`, `gauge.h`, `counter.h`, `exposer.h` | Forward to `simpleapi.h` |
| `nlohmann/json.hpp` | Minimal JSON stub |
| `ifaddrs.h` | Empty POSIX stub (lwIP lacks `getifaddrs`) |
| `sys/un.h` | `sockaddr_un`, `AF_UNIX`, `PF_UNIX` (ESP32 has no Unix domain sockets) |

## Port Implementations

All under `/project/components/zerotier_node/port/`:

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `zt_mutex.cpp` | `Mutex::lock/unlock` via `xSemaphoreTake/Give` |
| `zt_utils_esp.cpp` | `Utils::getSecureRandom` via `esp_fill_random` |
| `zt_metrics_esp.cpp` | Defines all `extern` symbols from `Metrics.hpp` as empty instances |
| `zt_bond_esp.cpp` | `Bond` constructors + `recordOutgoingPacket`, `getAppropriatePath`, `createBond`, `destroyBond`, `processBackgroundTasks`, etc. |
| `zt_trace_esp.cpp` | All `Trace` methods: `networkFilter`, all `credentialRejected` overloads, `incomingNetworkAccessDenied`, etc. |
| `zt_storage_esp.cpp` | NVS-backed state storage for ZeroTier identity and peer data |
| `zt_socket_esp.cpp` | lwIP UDP socket on port 9993, FreeRTOS receive task |
| `zt_tap_esp.cpp` | `virtualNetworkFrameFunction` and `virtualNetworkConfigFunction` callbacks (Phase 2 вЂ” logs frames only, no esp_netif attachment yet) |

