## Test Procedure

### Verify ESP32-S3 build

```bash
cd /project
idf.py build 2>&1 | tail -5
# Expected: "zt_esp32.bin binary size 0x... bytes. ... free."
# Failure: "dram0.bss overflowed" в†’ linker fragment not working
```

### Verify QEMU build and execution

```bash
# Build (set EXTRA_CPPFLAGS first вЂ” see above)
cd /qemu-project && idf.py build

# Run QEMU (see run command above)

# Expected serial output:
# I (xxxx) zt_qemu: IP: 10.0.2.15              в†ђ Ethernet + DHCP working
# I (xxxx) zt_qemu: ZT_Node_new rc=0 node=...  в†ђ Node created successfully
# I (xxxx) zt_qemu: ZT event: 6                в†ђ ZT_EVENT_ONLINE
```

### Size analysis

```bash
cd /project   # or /qemu-project
idf.py size-components 2>/dev/null | grep -E 'zerotier|Total'
```

